      },
      {
        "segment": "It is our native earth and the rapidity of the progress of the mind/body/spirit complexes upon its surface was due to harmonious interaction.",
        "start_offset": 499,
        "end_offset": 640,
        "start": 125.724,
        "end": 159.625
      },
      {
        "segment": "Upon the entity known to you as Mars, as you have already discussed, this entity was stopped in mid-third density, thus being unable to continue in progression due to the lack of hospitable conditions upon the surface.",
