        "end_offset": 859,
        "start": 162.885,
        "end": 215.467
      },
      {
        "segment": "This planet shall be undergoing healing for some of your space/time millennia.",
        "start_offset": 860,
        "end_offset": 938,
        "start": 216.667,
        "end": 233.548
      },
      {
        "segment": "The planet which you dwell upon has a metaphysical history well known to you and you may ask about it if you wish.",
        "start_offset": 939,
        "end_offset": 1053,
        "start": 236.168,
        "end": 263.248
      },
      {
        "segment": "However, we have spoken to a great degree upon this subject.",
